---
title: Grilled Roman Chicken with Tomato and Herb Salad
description: This Italian-inspired dish is a lighter meal, perfect for those hot summer nights. Dig in to juicy marinated chicken, grilled tomatoes, ciabatta, fresh torn basil, and the perfect sprinkling of Parmesan. That's amore!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grilled-roman-chicken-f1158878.jpg
